<%# A time chapter in Rewind — "This month", "March", "2024" — and how many
    highlights it holds. The "time frame highlight" that marks each leg of the
    journey back, set off by the timeline's hairline. `label` and `count` locals. %>
<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2.5 pt-9 pb-1">
  <h3 class="text-[15px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground"><%= label %></h3>
  <span class="text-[12px] font-medium text-muted-foreground"><%= t("home.index.rewind_count", count: count) %></span>
</div>
